#

Grilled Herb-Crusted Rack of Lamb

$45
650 kcal
Difficulty: 75%

Allergens:

Lamb

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

ElegantFine DiningSpecial Occasion

Description

A succulent rack of lamb, grilled to perfection with a fragrant herb crust, served with a velvety red wine reduction.

Ingredients

  • Rack of lamb: 1 (8-bone)
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Red wine: 1 cup
  • Beef stock: 1 cup
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
